Welcome to My City Sweet Home and explore your new house in the urban area! Play some fun city games for kids all day and enjoy creating your own stories!

Meet My City family members and role play with mom, dad, kids, their neighbors, and with many other dolls in this amazing dollhouse game for kids!

MY CITY FUN HOME GAME – COOL GAME FOR GIRLS AND BOYS!

Check all the rooms in this dollhouse! Each room offers many opportunities for you to play! You will need only your creativity and imagination to create your own doll story! the entire apartment the way you like and play dress-up games all day! Interact with almost everything as all the items can be moved! Visit your neighbors and check what they are doing and find more ways to have fun!

IMAGINE AND CREATE FAMILY STORIES YOU LIKE

Enjoy cool family home games: prepare food in the kitchen, decorate your new apartment, and choose funny hairstyles for all characters! Fun is everywhere in My City Home dollhouse!

My City Fun Christmas Home game allows you to create your own family life story! Win gifts and prizes daily! Everything is possible in our Apartment Dollhouse game as each room has different toys for you to play with!


MY CITY SWEET HOME FEATURES:

• Meet My City Home family and role play games all day! 
• 12 city locations including 2 apartments and a clothing store
• New characters: 2 families with kids, babies, neighbors, and others
• Play My City games with no stress! There is no competition, just fun
• Dress up games - customize characters and all dollhouse rooms as you like
• Explore My City Apartment and find a hidden treasure
• Make the best PARTY ever! Celebrate your birthday and invite your friends
• Meet your neighbors and play games on the street
• Buy ice cream for you and your friend
• Daily gifts and prizes

Can you find the two baby kittens hiding in this game? Will you fix the leaking water pipe? Adventure and fun can be found everywhere in the My City game! While playing this game kids will improve their creativity and imagination! There are no levels in this game only fun and endless opportunities for kids to create their own stories!

Let’s make the best birthday party ever in the living room! Simply throw the pizza in the oven, turn on the disco ball and let the music play. With so many rooms and characters, you will have a lot of fun!

Move objects, explore all rooms or go outside and play on the street! Discover hidden objects and win rewards! Choose a perfect dress or a shirt for all dolls! You can dress dolls the way you like!

MY CITY APARTMENT PLAYHOUSE – PLAY GAME FOR KIDS

Many new characters, rooms, clothing, and super cool accessories waiting for you! Choose a perfect outfit for your character to look nice! Invite your friend and play games on the same device! Yes, a multitouch option is available!

My City games are specially designed to foster kids' creativity and imagination as they have all the options in our games needed for creative expression. Kids need time for imaginative play and our games offer them the freedom to make their own decisions and ideas!

AGE GROUP
Kids games for 4-12 years old. My Town Family games are safe to play even when parents are not at home
